*Considerations*

- There is contradition with the modern mythological accounts of the greys as cogently morpho-ontical (all beings of emergent experience are the same whether good or bad)and the erception of spiritually advancing beings
- Current exo-mythological and astro-archiological estimations posit that “those with matter, matter.” Insinuating that the current Higher consciousness integrations are failing in majority of cases to be materializable as they act for sake of human proximity.
